title: Document pm-linked-test-adapters package in EXTENSIONS.md and TESTING.md
description: "packages/pm-linked-test-adapters exists as a first-party bundled package (pm-linked-test-adapters, version 0.1.0), but it is not mentioned anywhere in docs/EXTENSIONS.md, docs/TESTING.md, or docs/COMMANDS.md. The EXTENSIONS.md bundled-package catalog lists pm-beads, pm-todos, pm-lifecycle-hooks, pm-search-advanced but omits pm-linked-test-adapters, pm-calendar, pm-templates, and pm-guide-shell from the exemplar list."
